340
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:47,559
then you feel inferior to them...

341
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:49,511
and if they're lower,
you're too good for them...

342
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:52,200
so you end up spending the rest
