352
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,674
Who is it?

353
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:37,473
What am I supposed to tell them, Mort?
She's my sister.

354
00:23:37,600 --> 00:23:39,909
She didn't ask to stumble
onto an international incident.

355
00:23:40,040 --> 00:23:43,953
