00:25:24,280 --> 00:25:26,748
- You've got them, you've got the tickets.
- I don't have them.

381
00:25:26,880 --> 00:25:28,871
- There. I have them.
- Yeah. Thank you.

382
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:30,672
- Ticket, please.
- Hi.

383
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:35,471
The package will be on the plane.

384
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:42,517
Does that mean...

385
00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:48,912
- That was like a spy movie.
