386
00:25:50,080 --> 00:25:52,719
Look at you, you're just all
satisfied with yourself.

387
00:25:52,840 --> 00:25:53,795
Are you?

388
00:25:54,600 --> 00:25:55,919
Thank you.

389
00:25:56,280 --> 00:25:57,952
I couldn't have done it without you.

390
00:26:00,320 --> 00:26:02,834
That was like a spy movie. God.

391
00:26:03,040 --> 00:26:04,234
Thank you.

392
00:26:06,480 --> 00:26:07,515
Hi, Craig.

393
00:26:10,560 --> 00:26:13,757
<i>By the fall of 1984,</i>
<i>we could finally afford to move...</i>

394
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:16,553
<i>and Milly and I found a great old place</i>
<i>in Chevy Chase.</i>

395
00:26:16,680 --> 00:26:19,478
<i>A dream house,</i>
